---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us — The Dispatch"
  description="The Dispatch is an independent news publication committed to original reporting and honest analysis."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="page-label fade-up">About</div>
        <h1 class="page-title fade-up">
          Independent journalism<br />that doesn't ask permission.
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <div class="page-body">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="lead fade-up">
          The Dispatch was founded in 2022 on a simple premise: that the world
          needs more journalism that is accountable to readers, not advertisers,
          political sponsors, or engagement algorithms.
        </div>

        <div class="prose fade-up">
          <p>
            We cover the stories that matter — geopolitics, technology, science,
            business, and culture — with the depth and rigour they deserve. Our
            writers are experts and generalists, insiders and outsiders. What
            they share is a commitment to getting things right and explaining
            why they matter.
          </p>

          <h2>What we believe</h2>
          <p>
            Good journalism is not neutral. It takes facts seriously, follows
            them wherever they lead, and is willing to reach conclusions. It is
            fair to all sides without pretending that all sides are equal. It is
            written for readers who want to understand the world, not just be
            entertained by it.
          </p>

          <p>
            We are editorially independent. No government, corporation, or
            political party funds or influences our reporting. Our revenue comes
            from subscriptions and a small number of carefully selected
            advertising partners who have no influence over editorial decisions.
          </p>

          <h2>Our team</h2>
          <p>
            The Dispatch is built on a distributed model. Our editors are based
            in London, New York, and Singapore. Our contributors write from more
            than twenty countries. We believe that proximity to the story
            matters — and that the best coverage of Southeast Asia doesn't come
            from a bureau in Washington.
          </p>

          <h2>Our standards</h2>
          <p>
            We correct errors promptly and transparently. We name sources
            whenever possible and explain when we cannot. We distinguish clearly
            between news reporting and opinion. We do not publish stories we
            cannot verify.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you believe we have made an error, please contact us at <a
              href="mailto:corrections@thedispatch.com"
              >corrections@thedispatch.com</a
            >. We take corrections seriously.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-stats fade-up">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">40k+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Daily readers</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">20+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Countries covered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">2022</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Founded</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Independent</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }
  .page-header {
    padding: 64px 0 48px;
  }
  .page-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .page-body {
    padding: 48px 0 80px;
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-2);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-style: italic;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .prose {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 2em 0 0.7em;
    padding-bottom: 0.5em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .prose a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .prose a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border-light);
  }
  .stat-item {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container-narrow {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
